text.tspan: · Rim a rocks glass with the Serrano Lime Rimming Mixture.
· In a cocktail shaker with ice add:
- ¼ of a Serrano pepper, roughly chopped
· Shake vigorously and strain into the rimmed rocks glass.
· Rim a rocks glass with the Jalapeño Lime Rimming Mixture.
· In a cocktail shaker with ice add:
- ⅛ of a Jalapeño pepper, roughly chopped
· Shake vigorously and strain into the rimmed rocks glass.
